- Installasi Breeze -> berguna untuk alternatif dari laravel/ui (deprecated) / jetstream/fortify -> simple starting for authetication
    - composer require laravel/breeze --dev
    - php artisan breeze:Install
    - npm install && npm run dev
    - to activate forgot password using smtp gmail
        -> activate 2-step verification gmail (https://www.google.com/landing/2step/)
        -> Create App Password to be use by your system (https://security.google.com/settings/security/apppasswords)
        -> select others name for app testing
        -> use the generated password in env

